{"type": "article", "id": 30129, "title": "Raf Simons定档CK，以及，Tory Burch有款包不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-26T04:15:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 70, "name": "财报"}, {"id": 2593, "name": "美妆"}, {"id": 7705, "name": "眼影"}, {"id": 12512, "name": "维密天使"}, {"id": 14917, "name": "秋季"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 2882, "name": "Tory Burch"}, {"id": 15800, "name": "Lee"}, {"id": 30645, "name": "VF 集团"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 7113, "name": "Kanye West"}, {"id": 19775, "name": "Kylie Jenner"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016072611060593FDGH6KYWOQAUmJ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/ready-to-wear-sportswear/lvmh-sell-donna-karan-giii-apparel-group-10495621/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团把 Donna Karan 卖给了 G-III</b></a>｜美国 G-III 服装集团与 LVMH 集团达成收购协议，确认以 6.5 亿美元收购 LVMH 旗下品牌 Donna Karan 及其副线 DKNY。预计交易将在 2016 年底至次年初完成。2001 年 LVMH 集团以 6.43 亿美元收购了 Donna Karan。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/VF-Corp-meets-revenue-expectations-in-Q2-adjusts-year-outlook,717062.html#.V5a7xYQrJQZ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>VF 集团发布二季度财报</b></a>｜VF 集团发布了 2016 财年二季度财报，表现符合预期，收入上涨了 1% 至 24 亿美元，户外品类收益上涨了 2% 至 14 亿美元、牛仔品类则有 3% 的增长达到 6.29 亿美元。其中 North Face、Vans、Wrangler 和 Lee 牛仔的收益分别上涨 2%、4%、2% 和 8%，但 Timberland 有 7% 的跌幅。运动装品类下滑 19% 至 1.15 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Raf-Simons-to-start-at-Calvin-Klein-August-2,717151.html#.V5a-NYQrJQY\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Raf Simons 上任 Calvin Klein 日期确定</b></a>｜经过数月的谣言和等待， Calvin Klein  最近终于确认比利时设计师 Raf Simons 的上任日期，即 8 月 2 日。早前在 4 月 Calvin Klein 委婉证实了 Simons 将加入的消息，六月又表示设计师正在与另一品牌处理合同问题。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/balmain-fall-2016-campaign-kanye-west-joan-smalls-10496060/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Kanye West 为 Balmain 拍最新广告</b></a>｜Balmain 2016 秋季广告找来了“侃爷”Kanye West ，今天早些时候品牌 Instagram 主页发布了一张 Kanye West 和 Joan Smalls 共同拍摄的黑白照片，透露了这一消息。此前“卡戴珊家族”的卡戴珊本人、Kendall 和 Kylie Jenner 都为 Balmain 拍摄过大片。</p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726100249TUgdi1NxbY48DqPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">法国品牌 Iro 与波兰超模 Anja Rubik 、零售商 Boutique 1 <a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/news/boutique-1-launches-capsule-collection-with-iro-an.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">合作了一个胶囊系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726110158N60TvsqAIyL7mzSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.218750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261101590UO9rSJ4yZvMQgw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.218750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726110200EZk36YPzutglX9JQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.187500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726110201JwNIWjVx4t1XBH3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.218750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726110201hGdRkC1EAX9WrZUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.218750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>瑞典品牌 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/cos-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">COS 发布 2016 秋冬广告</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261042176XhAowRWl5NfHkZp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104220ANpVcfZrJDtBz7ej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682243\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104220oeYFtCQWf3EmPzRq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682470\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104221YzxWh9yq8ZiHXaD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682243\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104222DVPsTRex59fYW1ou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682243\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.whowhatwear.com/chloe-fall-2016-campaign/slide7\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chloé 的秋季广告</a>也不错：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104341ZUpA7yuOBqtP0nXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104341sAvBLGuDawKlFcCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104341hQrJyFsH8m7qMk5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104342l0AnrZTieuW3QKkb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104343ChDFtJNOakswXfqb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650350\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p style=\"text-align: left;\">科罗拉多超模&nbsp;<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/07/taylor-hill-topshop-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Taylor Hill 为 Topshop 拍摄秋季广告</a>，自 2014 年亮相维密秀后，Taylor 至今已为 Juicy Couture、Versus Versace、Ports 1961、Miu Miu 拍摄过大片，以及为 Fendi、Chanel、Givenchy 等品牌走秀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104010rIesEjpBnxJDfcQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.125000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104010jNdu5a4JEHzVeo9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104010o3YsfCmQWZ2UNK6i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.288750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Kylie Jenner 的美妆品牌此前的唇妆产品极受欢迎，近日<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/07/kylie-jenner-kyshadow-palette\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布了首款眼部产品 Kyshadow 眼影盘</a>，九个中性、棕色系的颜色：<br></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261040483DXZmnCBRIhg5rpY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.456116\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" class=\"\">Pharrell Williams 与 Adidas 合作的 Hu NMD 系列球鞋，推出<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/07/26/pharrell-adidas-nmd-human-race-red/#slide-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">全新红色配色</a>：<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104804CkUMa1uDo7sdVIrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104805xayl60p4sTj5AfMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726104807xY6KzZ5VFTpSy3b2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261048085esJEYkTKgt3vSzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Tory Burch 秋冬季新品推出<a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/accessories/must-have-tory-burch-introduces-the-gemini-link-ha.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">一款 Gemini Link 包袋</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726105339VX2i0tIqCmvlS3RL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261053439c6FuDCKrvxjwESe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261053471ukN9CtoODreWMPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607261054184alJuDekjp5hyTYx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p style=\"text-align: left;\" class=\"\"><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><p></p></div>"}